{"tid":1846910,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"口罩耗盡足以令社會癱瘓","createTime":"2020-01-27T19:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T21:21:51.000Z","uid":173326,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"28785d40976ac42f5b015378c50c21f833c359d5","tid":1846910,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:20:03.000Z","msg":"10號風後交通癱瘓，港豬提早出門，行路返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多處示威區域出現路障塞車，港豬親手清路、人力推巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎傳入香港，路面交通暢順，一半港豬怕返工、搭車染病，請假匿埋屋企，冇咩事都唔出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情持續，所有口罩耗盡，所有港豬唔敢踏出門口半步，冇人願意返工/返學/做生意，社會癱瘓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c488b8b5904b629f3c3dbf881a8b4dfc23137119","tid":1846910,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:22:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af97ad4f9f71507809a9cc9e9e7488c33f81ebf5","tid":1846910,"uid":92353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:48:00.000Z","msg":"林鄭將香港商界推入萬劫不復境界"},{"pid":"17a79003e8804aab65f0dc2ef8b4d51fc2395015","tid":1846910,"uid":60410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:15:15.000Z","msg":"冇gear 醫護唔可以開工<br />\n保險唔包"},{"pid":"47cedf0abbf9ec7035a22ef00a46d36543b060a2","tid":1846910,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17a79003e8804aab65f0dc2ef8b4d51fc2395015","tid":1846910,"uid":60410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:15:15.000Z","msg":"冇gear 醫護唔可以開工<br />\n保險唔包"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:21:51.000Z","msg":"放心<br />\n醫院會狗到叫你重用gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}